%p
  You are being sent this email because an attempt was made to login to your
  account at Tapjoy.com from a computer or device that was not recognized by our system.
  The request was made from #{@location} at #{@timestamp}.
  If it is you who is trying to access your account on this device then you
  can enter the verification number below into the appropriate box at Tapjoy.com.

%p
  Verification Key:
  %b= @verification_key

%p
  Verifying your account by email helps to protect us in the case that an attacker
  manages to get their hands on your account credentials for Tapjoy.com.  You can help by
  ensuring that your password for this email account is not the same as the one you use to
  login to the website.  If you have any questions, feel free to email dev@tapjoy.com.

%p
  %b
    If you did not attempt to access Tapjoy.com from a new computer or device your account may have been compromised.
    Please click the link below to block the device and and change your password.

%p
  %b= link_to("Block device and reset password", @block_link)
